[[Afaylu:Berber Calendars.jpg|thumb|250x250px|Asggʷas amaziɣ ɣ udlis]]'''Asggʷas amaziɣ''' niɣ Tafada tamaziɣt ({{Tifinaɣ| '''ⵜⴰⴼⴰⴷⴰ ⵜⴰⵎⴰⵣⵉⵖⵜ (ⴰⵙⴳⴳⴰⵙ ⴰⵎⴰⵣⵉⵖ) ⵏⵉⵖ ⵜⴰⴼⴰⴷⴰ ⵜⴰⵎⵕⵕⵓⴽⵉⵜ ⵏ ⵜⴰⵢⵔⵣⴰ'''}}). Asggas amaziɣ yan ɣ isggasn n ufgan llid izwarn urta illa wisa . Ar ittizwir ɣ was 13 innayr n umaḍlan . ar ttinin imaziɣ mas ar ttaran z was lli ikcm ugllid [[Cacnak|Cancaq]] tamazirt n ifrwawniyn. d lliɣ isndda tawja tis 22 n ifrεawnin ɣ tamurt n [[Miṣra ]]tamzwarut. Asggas amaziɣ ittyagal s wakal d mayyakka.

Ar sfuglun imaziɣn ussan ad s ukccum n usggʷas wiss 2971, d ar ittusnfal wakud n usfuglu s tffugla ya d gr ussan n sin d mraw d kṛaḍ d mraw ɣ yennayr.

D ar ttinin imassann n umzruy mas-d asfuglu s usggʷas amaziɣ iga asmkti s ukttuy n tnrawt n ugllid amaziɣ Cicanq f ugllid n ifirεawnin Ramsis wiss kṛaḍ ɣ imnɣi lli yemsarn ɣ ugmmaḍ n wasif n nnil ɣ usggʷas n 950 dat n tlalit n Ɛisa. d nttan ad igan imnɣi lliɣ issnta Cicanq anbaḍ n tgldit tafirεawnit ɣ twja ttis snat tmrawin d snat. D illa ma yesiwrrayn taffugla ya d n yiḍ innayer s usggʷas ayrzan ɣikan af ar ttussaɣ ula s usggʷas ayerzan, ar ttssnn t tiffugliwin s yixf n usggʷas amaziɣ tiṛwitin tussnawin. ittuẓlan s ku tasga d ku awank ɣ iwunak n yiẓẓlmḍ n tfṛiqt tugtt nnsn t zdint d tyrza.

D ar ttmun d tffugla ya d ula tinawin d tilalin tikadimin s uwttas n usissen s tɣrma tamaziɣt d umzruy nns, d ar isgdal ula tisumrin  izdin d imaziɣn d tmyurin nnsn d tussna nnsn taqbuṛt. Ar sfuglun imaziɣn s yiḍ innayer d yixf n usggʷas amaziɣ s kigan n tiram d tmyurin ittuẓlan s ku tasga.

Zzɣ timyurin n yixef n ussgʷas amaziɣ ɣ kra n tmnaḍin ɣ tmurt nnɣ ar ssrusn imkrazen ikuṛayen ɣzzifnin n uɣanim ɣ igran d tbḥirin nnsn arazaɣ s usggʷas ayerzan iɣudan d a gis ifk bab n yignwan uluɣ nns, tizi lliɣ ar ttbbin wazzann ijjign d ar lssan timlsa timaynutin ...

D ar ittɣama iwiz f urkez n uḥwac d tzlatin n ṛṛwayes, d ar skarn t tmɣarin timaziɣin mnnawet tiram mmimnin ɣ tffugla yad zund "Tagʷlla" d "Urkimen" d "Brkukc"  d "Sksu nɣd ibrin" d "ubaddaz" d kigan n tiram yaḍni ... d llan tasgiwin yaḍni ar qqṛsen i yifullusn d ar ssnwan tifyyi nnsn ɣ yiḍ ad. D tssikz tmurt n ddzayer s yixef n usggʷas amaziɣ mas iga tanuṛẓmt tanamurt zzɣ asggʷas n 2016.

Amma ɣ Umṛṛuk ar sul ttqqlen imɣnasn imaziɣn d ku imaziɣn s uwank a yessikz s yixf n usggʷas amaziɣ ad ig tanuṛẓmt tanamurt.

